======================================
FPDF

PDF generation with the FPDF library

by Jd Fiscus
======================================

Hey everybody,

This is a Codeigniter library where generate a PDF 
using the FPDF 1.7 library.

DOCUMENTATION:
http://www.fpdf.org/ > Manual

INSTALLATION:
Just copy the files from this package to the corresponding folder in your 
application folder.  For example, copy fpdf/libraries/fpdf.php to 
system/application/libraries/fpdf.php. 



Thanks,
-Jd Fiscus
